competence, of decent behavior _ was what the Sex Pistols were all
about. In case you thought the passage of time and the putative
coarsening of popular culture had dulled the group's ferocity,
``The Filth and the Fury,'' Julien Temple's electrifying new
documentary, will make you think again. Reviewed by A.O. Scott.
