remain in the United States fail. By Rick Bragg. (Meeting scheduled
for 4:30 p.m. EST.) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   DDT-OCEAN (Los Angeles) _ Taking the first steps toward
controlling the largest known site of DDT contamination in the
country, the Environmental Protection Agency is expected to
announce a multimillion-dollar program Wednesday to cap parts of
the deposit, which lies deep in the Pacific Ocean off the Southern
California coast.
</P>
<P>
   CELLPHONE-RECYCLE (New York) _ New York City plans to collect
used cell phones, reprogram them to dial an emergency helpline and
distribute them to victims of domestic violence, the elderly,
