Maybe it's wishful thinking since I'm a sucker for all things
Britpop, but I've got a feeling that 2000 will be year in which the
U.K.'s jangly psychedelia stages another siege on these shores. By
JANE GANAHL.
</P>
<P>
   TV-ER (Undated) _ ``ER'' has been the most dominant drama on
television since it debuted. With two other hospital dramas already
on the schedule _ ``Chicago Hope'' and ``City of Angels'' _ a cynic
might say a fourth is overkill. By TIM GOODMAN.
