<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-29 16:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1266 &Cx1f; taf-z
u l BC-HOME-IMPROVEMENT-ART-     03-29 0800
