<P>
   UGANDA-CULT (Rugazi, Uganda) _ Another 53 bodies were discovered
Wednesday crammed into a small pit inside the house of one of the
Uganda cult leaders. A total of 81 bodies have been found in the
pit in the last two days, 48 of them children. With each day
bringing some new horror, the police said Wednesday night that they
suspected yet another mass grave at a building about 50 miles south
of here, in the southwest of Uganda. Excavation will begin on
Thursday morning, the police said. By Ian Fisher.
</P>
