   KOSOVO-CONGRESS (Washington) _ After a rancorous debate, the
House is expected to approve late Wednesday night a $13 billion
spending bill that includes emergency aid for Colombia to combat
drug traffickers and for the military to pay for its peacekeeping
mission in Kosovo. By Eric Schmitt.
</P>
