<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-29 18:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1436 &Cx1f; taf-z
u e BC-SHANA-MORRISON-NYT &LR;      03-29 0465
