daunting. If a computer is more than a couple of years old, it may
well need to be replaced by a new one before dictation software can
be used successfully. Even a newer computer may need more RAM or a
better sound card. And picking out a software program and learning
how to use it well means an investment of time. (Tony Cenicola/The
New York Times)
